Show HN: Got tired of filling out PDFs so I built a tool to turn them into forms
text:
The title says it all! Curious to hear any feedback or if any folks on here would find it useful!

Here's a demo video: https://www.loom.com/share/02f7b5cec8104110a95dad8640aae3b4

I learned a ton about building with PDFs in the process, so if anyone wants to chat about PDF + workflow tools give me a shout as well -- would love to connect!
